## SDD Workflow at a Glance

阶段:**W0 Bootstrap → W1 Change → W2 Review & Archive → W3 Steer**。

Phase | Commands
---|---
W0 Bootstrap | `/hx-constitution` `/hx-baseline`
W1 Change | `/hx-propose` `/hx-clarify` `/hx-design` `/hx-plan` `/hx-tasks` `/hx-analyze` `/hx-implement` `/hx-verify`
W2 Review & Archive | `/hx-review` `/hx-archive`
W3 Steer | `/hx-doctor`
Routing | `/hx-next` (suggests next command + flow)

Flow 等级控制流程繁简:**`{{ flow }}` 是本项目的默认值**。
- `quick` —— bugfix / 小重构:implement → verify → review → archive
- `standard` —— 常规特性(默认):propose → plan → tasks → implement → verify → review → archive
- `full` —— 跨切面 / API / 安全相关:+ clarify + design + analyze + ADR
- `epic` —— 多能力联动:拆分,子任务按 full / standard 运行

